item.title: Fake servers on status checker(won't log in again )
item.dc:creator: @Slave_Scyth Slave Scyth
item.description:
@Slave_Scyth wrote:

The Servers only have to be online when the Owner puts them on the list, they aren’t Online all the time. If the Server’s we’re Online for a long time there’s a good chance it’s going to take them a long time to get off the list.
